{"id": "1473982519350132839", "channel_id": "1473982519350132839", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "The Gaze intention, that will be performed by each mob, in astral reign, after turn 6, penalize very slow teams that need to build up counter to dispatch of them, and at a certain point, counter teams just can't kill them anymore, because Gaze don't attack, so it doesn't proc the counter.\n\nI ask if this Intention could be changed to at least attack for 1 damage, so that counter teams that are majorly focused on slow stacking and defense can still play the game.", "timestamp": "2026-02-19T10:00:17.884000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "shock", "emoji_id": "1356053145427640483", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Nautila_think", "emoji_id": "1459077762684948500", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1473982519664836681", "filename": "ss-.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 51927, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1473982519350132839/1473982519664836681/ss-.png?ex=69cc43f1&is=69caf271&hm=2d60990789232c186c7c56a05b3747aac692021b2ea275f58d3d9ce3ed4807c5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1473982519350132839", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Possible change to the Gaze intention", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
